    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/5fd7ceb9b7ad3ab2aeff9e79943acdf2.poster.avif?t=1771879351\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/5fd7ceb9b7ad3ab2aeff9e79943acdf2.webm?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/5fd7ceb9b7ad3ab2aeff9e79943acdf2.mp4?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>星际之旅</strong> 邀请您扮演Max，一个在被人类遗弃的荒凉地球上幸存下来的人。凭借您遗忘的过去和新发现的非凡能力，踏上一项重塑Gaia人类命运的使命。<br><br>当您探索广阔的宇宙时，生存、战斗、探索和个性化交织在一起，带来独一无二的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/8a492d1aeaf20b95ee3f789df24b9c76.poster.avif?t=1771879351\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/8a492d1aeaf20b95ee3f789df24b9c76.webm?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/8a492d1aeaf20b95ee3f789df24b9c76.mp4?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主要特点：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>探索庞大的宇宙：</strong>在5个吸引人的星系中穿越2万个按程序生成的行星。每次旅程都会带来新的发现、冒险和挑战。<br></li><li> <strong>参与激动人心的战斗：</strong>与敌对势力交战，掌控海盗船只，并使用独特的按程序生成武器定制您的武器库。<br></li><li> <strong>生存和资源管理：</strong>通过管理睡眠、饥饿、健康和能量水平来确保在严酷的世界中生存。<br></li><li> <strong>时尚旅行：</strong>驾驶您的飞船穿越星系，在悬浮摩托车上快速穿越广阔的行星景观。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/f68741e000b8a2acbb78438a818254ea.poster.avif?t=1771879351\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/f68741e000b8a2acbb78438a818254ea.webm?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/f68741e000b8a2acbb78438a818254ea.mp4?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>解开谜团并获得新的飞船：</strong>解决古老的谜题，增强您的属性，并获得新的船只进行探索。<br></li><li> <strong>塑造您的居住空间：</strong>在行星上定居，并通过创意定制选项塑造您理想的居住空间。根据波动的市场趋势进行房地产交易。<br></li><li> <strong>复杂的对话系统：</strong>与各种物种互动，每个物种都有独特的故事，培养有意义的联系和关系。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/31ac7e0e687d8e68ac90c8f1007ed00f.poster.avif?t=1771879351\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/31ac7e0e687d8e68ac90c8f1007ed00f.webm?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2329800/extras/31ac7e0e687d8e68ac90c8f1007ed00f.mp4?t=1771879351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>个性化您的飞船：</strong>不仅为美观而且为了在行星外战斗中获得优势，定制您的飞船内部。<br></li><li> <strong>引人入胜的叙事：</strong>沉浸于一个随您每个决策而演变的叙事，一个超越死亡的故事。</li></ul><br>准备好在遥远的星星中重新发现人类的潜力。Gaia的未来掌握在您手中。您准备好迎接冒险了吗？",
